data.title: Parliamentarian Oded Forer: ‘Make Israel Normal Again’ (with VIDEO)
data.meta_description: In a TLV Internationals event moderated by The Media Line, parliamentarian Oded Forer, number two on the list for the Yisrael Beitenu party, spoke to a crowd of largely new immigrants about the September 17 national elections.
